<codeline lineno="94"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="95"><highlight class="comment">Add<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>content<sp/>to<sp/>/var/www/zorba.php:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="96"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="97"><highlight class="comment">\code</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="98"><highlight class="comment">&lt;html&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="99"><highlight class="comment">&lt;title&gt;Zorba<sp/>test&lt;/title&gt;</highlight></codeline>
